    <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
      <head>Biographical History</head>
      <p>Edwin T. Whiffen was a teacher in New York, and an author of plays, poems, translations, and non-fiction.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
      <head>Scope and Contents of the Collection</head>
      <p>The <emph render="bold">Edwin T. Whiffen Papers</emph> consists of manuscripts, including plays, poems, a translation of a Greek play, and 
	  unidentifiable material in manuscript form.</p>
    </scopecontent>
